Task Overview

Within the Stratos Datacenter, the Nautilus backup server stores template XML files required by the Nautilus application.
Before these templates can be used, placeholder strings must be replaced with valid data.

As part of routine maintenance, system administrators at xFusionCorp Industries use Linux string and file manipulation utilities to update such files efficiently.

